{"title":"Overview","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Overview"},"headingText":"Let's create a weekend playlist","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n<details>\n  <summary class=\"collapsible-section\"><div class=\"thePlan h3\">What</div></summary>\n  <strong>A weekend away.</strong> Leave on Saturday - Have fun - Eventually return home of Sunday.  \n  <h4>Current Scheme</h4>\n  <strong>Saturday</strong>\n  <ul><li>Pottery before lunch.</li>\n  <li>Got out for lunch.</li>\n  <li>'Check-in' to accomodation.</li>\n  <li>Beach afternoon.</li>\n  <li>Head back to accommodation and either get ready to go out for dinner or settle in and order food in.</li> \n  <li>Drinks / Games / Dancing</li></ul>\n  <strong>Sunday</strong>\n  <ul><li>Lazy morning! Sleep in and relax.</li>\n  <li>Eventually go out to brunch.</li>\n  <li><i>Eventually</i> head home.</li>\n  </ul>\n</details>\n<hr/>\n<details>\n  <summary class=\"collapsible-section\"><div class=\"thePlan h3\">Where</div></summary>\n  <strong>Sunshine Coast.</strong> Close enough that it isn't annoying to get to and get home but far enough that it is a change in environment.\n</details>\n<hr/>\n<details>\n  <summary class=\"collapsible-section\"><div class=\"thePlan h3\">When</div></summary>\n  <strong>End of October - beginning November.</strong> Hopefully enough time to plan and budget but not too close to the End of year / Christmas chaos.\n</details>\n\n\n\nSometimes finding the right music can be stressful (well, it is for me) so why not push everyone else into creating a playlist that combines all our music.  \nEveryone wins, right?\n\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" data-bs-toggle=\"offcanvas\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/playlist/5uwdCcZvOsJWnbdmml1ydm?si=GIdBRLPHTtacNOJ_QKupag&pi=KYkoE1B-QSuQi\" role=\"button\" aria-controls=\"offcanvasExample\" style=\"width: stretch;\">Add songs to the playlist</a>","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n<details>\n  <summary class=\"collapsible-section\"><div class=\"thePlan h3\">What</div></summary>\n  <strong>A weekend away.</strong> Leave on Saturday - Have fun - Eventually return home of Sunday.  \n  <h4>Current Scheme</h4>\n  <strong>Saturday</strong>\n  <ul><li>Pottery before lunch.</li>\n  <li>Got out for lunch.</li>\n  <li>'Check-in' to accomodation.</li>\n  <li>Beach afternoon.</li>\n  <li>Head back to accommodation and either get ready to go out for dinner or settle in and order food in.</li> \n  <li>Drinks / Games / Dancing</li></ul>\n  <strong>Sunday</strong>\n  <ul><li>Lazy morning! Sleep in and relax.</li>\n  <li>Eventually go out to brunch.</li>\n  <li><i>Eventually</i> head home.</li>\n  </ul>\n</details>\n<hr/>\n<details>\n  <summary class=\"collapsible-section\"><div class=\"thePlan h3\">Where</div></summary>\n  <strong>Sunshine Coast.</strong> Close enough that it isn't annoying to get to and get home but far enough that it is a change in environment.\n</details>\n<hr/>\n<details>\n  <summary class=\"collapsible-section\"><div class=\"thePlan h3\">When</div></summary>\n  <strong>End of October - beginning November.</strong> Hopefully enough time to plan and budget but not too close to the End of year / Christmas chaos.\n</details>\n\n\n# Let's create a weekend playlist \n\nSometimes finding the right music can be stressful (well, it is for me) so why not push everyone else into creating a playlist that combines all our music.  \nEveryone wins, right?\n\n<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" data-bs-toggle=\"offcanvas\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/playlist/5uwdCcZvOsJWnbdmml1ydm?si=GIdBRLPHTtacNOJ_QKupag&pi=KYkoE1B-QSuQi\" role=\"button\" aria-controls=\"offcanvasExample\" style=\"width: stretch;\">Add songs to the playlist</a>"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":fal